#: ../../en/configuration.rst:2
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "配置与 Workspace"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:4
msgid "AnnaAgent separates project code from runtime state. The repository contains the package, while each workspace contains configuration, secrets, generated states, logs, and memory indexes."
msgstr "AnnaAgent 将项目代码和运行状态分离。仓库中保存 package；每个 workspace 保存配置、密钥、生成状态、日志和本地记忆库。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:9
msgid "Workspace Files"
msgstr "Workspace 文件"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:11
msgid "``settings.yaml``"
msgstr "``settings.yaml``"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:12
msgid "Non-secret configuration such as base URLs, model names, feature flags, SFT endpoint settings, memory settings, and asset metadata."
msgstr "非密钥配置，例如 base URL、模型名、SFT endpoint、记忆设置和资产信息。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:15
msgid "``.env``"
msgstr "``.env``"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:16
msgid "Local secrets such as API keys. This file must not be committed."
msgstr "本地密钥，例如 API key。不要提交到 Git。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:18
msgid "``.env.example``"
msgstr "``.env.example``"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:19
msgid "Commented placeholders showing which environment variables can be used."
msgstr "注释形式的密钥占位符，方便手动配置。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:21
msgid "``assets/anna-assets.json``"
msgstr "``assets/anna-assets.json``"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:22
msgid "Manifest for HuggingFace repositories, direct-download assets, and local SFT model targets."
msgstr "HuggingFace 仓库、直接下载资源和本地 SFT 目标路径的 manifest。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:25
msgid "``cases/``"
msgstr "``cases/``"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:26
msgid "JSON or YAML case files used by CLI commands and batch runs."
msgstr "CLI 和 batch run 使用的 JSON/YAML 案例。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:28
msgid "``prompts/``"
msgstr "``prompts/``"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:29
msgid "Frozen prompt states and full initialization states."
msgstr "frozen prompt state 和 full initialization state。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:31
msgid "``runs/`` and ``logs/``"
msgstr "``runs/`` 与 ``logs/``"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:32
msgid "Experiment outputs, vLLM service PIDs, and service logs."
msgstr "实验输出、vLLM 服务 PID 和日志。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:35
msgid "Inspect and Edit Configuration"
msgstr "查看和修改配置"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:44
msgid "Use ``--no-redact`` only on a trusted terminal because it can reveal local configuration values. API keys should be entered through ``anna config secrets`` or stored in ``.env``."
msgstr "只有在可信终端中才使用 ``--no-redact``。API key 建议通过 ``anna config secrets`` 输入，或者写入 workspace 的 ``.env``。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:49
msgid "Model Modes"
msgstr "模型模式"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:51
msgid "AnnaAgent has three practical model modes."
msgstr "AnnaAgent 常用三种模型模式。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:53
msgid "Backbone/base model mode"
msgstr "Backbone/base model 模式"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:54
msgid "The simplest mode. AnnaAgent internal modules call the configured backbone chat model. This model can temporarily stand in when no external counselor is wired, but formal runs should use a dedicated counselor process or model for counselor turns."
msgstr "最简单。AnnaAgent 内部模块会调用配置的 backbone chat model。没有外部 counselor 时，它可以临时代替 counselor 模型；正式运行时应使用专门的 counselor 流程或模型来生成 counselor 轮次。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:57
msgid "Configured SFT endpoint mode"
msgstr "已部署 SFT endpoint 模式"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:58
msgid "Use this when complaint-chain or emotion SFT models are already deployed as OpenAI-compatible services."
msgstr "如果你已经部署了 complaint 或 emotion SFT OpenAI-compatible 服务，用 ``models configure`` 写入地址。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:61
msgid "Local vLLM deployment mode"
msgstr "本地 vLLM 部署模式"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:62
msgid "Use this on Linux/GPU machines when AnnaAgent should start the SFT services for you and write the resulting endpoint configuration back to the workspace."
msgstr "在 Linux/GPU 机器上，让 AnnaAgent 自动启动 SFT 服务并写回 workspace 配置。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:65
msgid "Common commands:"
msgstr "常用命令："

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:79
msgid "Secrets and Safety"
msgstr "安全建议"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:81
msgid "Keep ``.env`` out of Git."
msgstr "不提交 ``.env``。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:82
msgid "Prefer environment variables or ``anna config secrets`` for API keys."
msgstr "API key 使用环境变量或 ``anna config secrets``。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:83
msgid "Use redacted output in issue reports and logs."
msgstr "公开 issue 和日志中只使用脱敏输出。"

#: ../../en/configuration.rst:84
msgid "Do not paste real counseling records into public issues or model prompts."
msgstr "不要把真实心理咨询记录粘贴到公开 issue 或公开模型 prompt 中。"
